Dialogue: 0,0:00:02.39,0:00:04.31,Main,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,I've had enough!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.31,0:00:07.27,Main,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,I can't study for the test any longer!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.27,0:00:08.40,Main,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go to the arcade.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:08.40,0:00:10.36,Main,Takao&Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,If you say so, I guess we have to.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.67,0:00:12.37,Main,Takao,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, let's go, Нисиката.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.69,0:00:15.70,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,You'll get stupid if you study too much.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:15.70,0:00:18.08,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'll study.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.30,0:00:19.33,Main,Takao,0000,0000,0000,,I see!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.75,0:00:21.55,Main,Takao,0000,0000,0000,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.88,0:00:24.22,Main,Kimura,0000,0000,0000,,Let's go play!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.22,0:00:26.00,Main,Sakurai,0000,0000,0000,,Which bishoujo figure are you getting?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.81,0:00:28.96,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn it... I'm jealous.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.19,0:00:33.84,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But! I have to get a good grade\Non my next test!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:33.84,0:00:36.32,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, can I sit here?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.52,0:00:42.77,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Studying for the test?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.77,0:00:44.21,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:24.99,0:02:29.00,Studying for the test,Title 1,0000,0000,0000,,Studying for the Test
Dialogue: 0,0:02:26.45,0:02:27.84,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,"Studying for the Test."
Dialogue: 0,0:02:29.30,0:02:32.24,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I passed by Takao-кун\Nand the others just now.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:33.15,0:02:36.22,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. We were all studying together.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.88,0:02:38.80,Night on the Galactic Railroad,Book,0000,0000,0000,,Night on the Galactic Railroad
Dialogue: 0,0:02:39.18,0:02:43.11,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,They were running out of here\N yelling, "Let's go play!"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.11,0:02:44.64,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You aren't going with them?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.22,0:02:47.48,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,I don't have time to play.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:48.65,0:02:52.02,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,If I don't score within the top \Nfifty of my grade,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.46,0:02:54.58,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,my parents are gonna\N confiscate my video games.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.31,0:02:58.37,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.99,0:03:04.75,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Oh, no! Why am I telling her everything?!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:04.75,0:03:08.41,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If I give her that info, she'll definitely\N interfere with my studying!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.28,0:03:15.04,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,J-Just kidding...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.19,0:03:17.09,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,About what?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:17.72,0:03:19.31,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,It's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:20.30,0:03:22.72,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,A-Anyway, no interruptions...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.11,0:03:26.49,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,That's mean. You say that like\N I'm always getting in your way or something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.49,0:03:27.75,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You are!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.57,0:03:29.43,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,That's because...
Dialogue: 0,0:03:30.99,0:03:33.33,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,it's fun to tease you, Нисиката.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:34.40,0:03:35.95,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Should I study somewhere else?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:35.95,0:03:39.32,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, if I do that, it'll be like\NI've let Такаги-сан win.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.83,0:03:45.20,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,You're not studying, Такаги-сан?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.86,0:03:49.82,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. I have a rule about \N studying only two hours a day.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.82,0:03:51.50,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:52.19,0:03:54.11,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I didn't expect anything less from Такаги-сан.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:54.11,0:03:56.71,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She can easily score in \Nthe top ten of our grade.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.66,0:04:00.45,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But... what is she thinking?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.45,0:04:02.70,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}This is Такаги-сан we're talking about,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.70,0:04:05.29,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm sure she's gonna do\N something to get in my way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.29,0:04:06.96,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}There's no way she won't.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:06.96,0:04:08.81,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Because she's Такаги-сан!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.63,0:04:10.85,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:10.85,0:04:12.91,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:13.42,0:04:15.41,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,I guess it's nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:15.41,0:04:18.29,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,I was just looking. It's not like—
Dialogue: 0,0:04:16.22,0:04:17.97,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, that one is wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:18.29,0:04:19.09,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.30,0:04:24.57,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Problem six, where it says\N"Solve for x over (-2 + 3y)."
Dialogue: 0,0:04:24.57,0:04:26.71,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? I got this wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.03,0:04:27.83,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:27.83,0:04:29.03,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.75,0:04:36.00,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Where? This is, uhh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.24,0:04:41.43,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Here we go.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.93,0:04:43.85,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Такаги-сан?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.35,0:04:50.10,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,It's easier for me to teach you this way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.43,0:04:55.81,Main Top,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,So, x equals -16 and y equals -1, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.12,0:04:55.81,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Такаги-сан is teaching me?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.16,0:04:58.27,Main Top,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,First, just substitute them as-is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.76,0:04:58.27,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What is she planning?!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.65,0:04:59.98,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Write out the formula.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:00.27,0:05:01.69,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Ah, okay...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.03,0:05:05.33,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,This will be a negative number\N times a negative number,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:05.33,0:05:07.02,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,so pay attention to the\N order of operations.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.02,0:05:09.16,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Oh! Then, the answer is...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.83,0:05:11.54,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,five.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.76,0:05:13.16,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, that's right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.80,0:05:15.04,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, and this...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:15.04,0:05:18.63,Italics,Nishiikata,0000,0000,0000,,Такаги-сан is amazing. She can\N figure it out at just a quick glance.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.66,0:05:22.59,Main,Nishiikata,0000,0000,0000,,Th-Thanks... I wasn't really getting this.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.09,0:05:25.88,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I'll just teach you from\N the beginning, then.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.84,0:05:31.22,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}T-Такаги-сан is gonna teach me?\N I'm saved!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:32.40,0:05:34.52,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No, something's fishy!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:34.88,0:05:38.42,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why is she being so nice?! It's odd!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:38.99,0:05:43.57,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,T-Такаги-сан, why are you\N being so nice to me today?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:44.01,0:05:45.48,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,What do you mean?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.22,0:05:50.28,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Well, you're kinda being\Nunusually nice today, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:52.81,0:05:57.33,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah... I'm always teasing you during class,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.81,0:06:00.45,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,so I'd feel bad if your grades go down\N because of me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:02.09,0:06:02.99,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Нисиката...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.46,0:06:06.05,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I'm sorry for teasing you every day.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.05,0:06:08.85,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Let's make sure you do well on the next test.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.99,0:06:12.14,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Такаги-сан...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.66,0:06:17.29,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You've finally changed your ways!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.29,0:06:20.43,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,All right! I'll do my best!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.15,0:06:24.67,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks for the juice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:24.67,0:06:25.98,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.98,0:06:29.66,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,I made huge progress\N on math today, thanks to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:30.22,0:06:32.74,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have a better chance\N of not getting my games confiscated.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.26,0:06:38.34,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Maybe Такаги-сан is actually a good person.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:39.45,0:06:41.54,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously, thanks for today, Такаги-сан.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:41.80,0:06:44.25,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You don't need to thank me.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.35,0:06:46.71,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,After all, what I taught you today
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.09,0:06:49.59,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,won't be on the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.10,0:06:56.82,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,H-Hey, wait!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.82,0:06:58.55,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You've mastered substitution, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.55,0:07:02.04,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,I did, but still!\NGive me back that juice!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.04,0:07:03.28,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, I opened it already.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:03.28,0:07:04.94,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,You just opened it now!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:04.94,0:07:07.94,Test,Title 2,0000,0000,0000,,Test
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.25,0:07:07.05,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,"Test."
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.31,0:07:10.21,Main-Tanabe,Танабэ,0000,0000,0000,,Pass the answer sheets forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.53,0:07:16.46,Italics,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,I think I did well. I should've gotten\N a ninety, at least.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.46,0:07:17.73,Italics,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,Good, good.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:18.91,0:07:20.27,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,Юкари-тян...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.27,0:07:21.51,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0000,0000,0000,,Can you teach this to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.29,0:07:24.60,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,English is not my cup of tea.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.60,0:07:27.49,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? You make it sound as though\N you're good at everything else.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.65,0:07:30.73,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,I meant it's my worst subject!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.73,0:07:33.84,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,Anyway, the translation for this—
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.77,0:07:38.68,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,Sorry, but I want to review as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.04,0:07:41.89,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?! But you always help me study!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:41.89,0:07:45.41,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,If I get ninety percent or above\N on all the tests this time,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.41,0:07:47.61,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,my parents will buy any video game I want!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.11,0:07:52.24,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,How do I turn this into a negative sentence?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:52.46,0:07:53.57,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,Were you listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.06,0:07:56.71,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,In any case, I don't have\N the time to teach you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.71,0:07:57.79,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,Meanie!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.75,0:08:01.84,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,Which is more important?\N A video game or friends?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.84,0:08:02.96,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.96,0:08:06.76,Main-Mina,Мина,0000,0000,0000,,You can play video games, but\N but you can't teach a video game!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.76,0:08:07.98,Main-Sanae,Санаэ,0000,0000,0000,,Right, right.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.08,0:08:13.89,Main-Yukari,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,Now that those nuisances\N are gone, I should review.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.41,0:08:17.35,Main-Tanabe,Танабэ,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I'm handing out the test now.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:17.61,0:08:19.14,Main-Tanabe,Танабэ,0000,0000,0000,,Pass it back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.74,0:08:22.91,Italics,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, I've thoroughly reviewed\N the subject before the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.58,0:08:23.30,Main-Tanabe,Танабэ,0000,0000,0000,,{\an8}Everyone got one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:23.30,0:08:26.57,Italics,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,I'll score above ninety percent\N on this English test as well!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.44,0:08:27.44,Black Signs,Test,0000,0000,0000,,First-year End of Term Test\NMath
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.44,0:08:28.79,Italics,Юкари,0000,0000,0000,,Math?!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:29.94,0:08:33.95,sign_12227_140_Returned_Test,Title 3,0000,0000,0000,,Test {\c&H3F30F8&}Results
Dialogue: 0,0:08:31.47,0:08:32.84,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,"Test Results."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.56,0:08:35.45,Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Here.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:35.76,0:08:37.69,Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Did you study at all?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.56,0:08:40.29,Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Saitou.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:40.99,0:08:42.58,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You look worried.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:43.05,0:08:44.05,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Not really...
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.05,0:08:45.07,Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Такаги.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:45.55,0:08:46.25,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.47,0:08:51.56,Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,You did well, as usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:54.68,0:08:56.68,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Такаги-тян, what did you get?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.08,0:08:58.55,Main,Girl,0000,0000,0000,,Can I see the answers later?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.11,0:09:01.77,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You got a good score?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.17,0:09:04.69,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, but not a hundred percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.95,0:09:08.37,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's Такаги-сан for you. But I should—
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.37,0:09:09.78,Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Next, Нисиката!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:09.78,0:09:10.92,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Yes, sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:13.12,0:09:14.92,Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,Do a little better next time, will ya?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.85,0:09:19.90,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Was it bad?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.88,0:09:22.69,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}As if you're so concerned!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:22.69,0:09:25.59,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You're the one who taught me\N stuff not covered on the test.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:25.59,0:09:28.43,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}You say that so casually only\N because you got a good score!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.65,0:09:29.41,Main Top,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Hey. I said, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:30.28,0:09:32.92,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Let's try to guess each other's score.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.55,0:09:34.91,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Whoever guesses closer wins.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.34,0:09:37.63,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,You always do stuff\N like this out of the blue.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.14,0:09:39.03,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I don't mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.79,0:09:42.66,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Umm... About fifty percent?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:45.81,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,You underestimate me too much, Такаги-сан.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.26,0:09:47.35,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I see.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.96,0:09:50.95,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Then, did you get above sixty percent?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.36,0:09:54.36,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,So it's below that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.23,0:09:56.45,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How did she know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:56.78,0:09:58.43,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Give her your poker face!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.43,0:10:01.13,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Confuse her with your poker face!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.63,0:10:03.19,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Did you get above fifty-five percent?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.51,0:10:07.50,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,It is.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.50,0:10:08.92,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Why?!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:09.31,0:10:12.38,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,So it's between fifty-five to fifty-nine.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.38,0:10:14.84,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to stop her from\N guessing the exact score.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:15.85,0:10:17.33,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Okay, then...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:18.52,0:10:20.15,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty-six.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:21.77,0:10:23.01,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty-seven?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:24.19,0:10:25.36,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty-eight?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:26.57,0:10:27.75,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Fifty-nine?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:29.35,0:10:31.69,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, I got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:32.65,0:10:34.15,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,It's fifty-six percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:34.86,0:10:37.66,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Is that your answer, Такаги-сан?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:37.66,0:10:38.36,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Yep.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.19,0:10:42.32,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,My test score is...
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.95,0:10:45.49,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,fifty-nine percent!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.83,0:10:48.50,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Sucks for you!\NYou were close, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:49.85,0:10:52.58,Main,Teacher,0000,0000,0000,,The only thing that sucks\Nis your test score.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:53.13,0:10:54.17,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,You're right, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:58.30,0:11:01.35,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Aww, I was off by three?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.25,0:11:06.31,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You guess my score now.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:06.67,0:11:09.56,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,If you're off within two percent, you win.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.93,0:11:13.27,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Okay! I'm gonna figure it out\N based on Такаги-сан's reaction!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.73,0:11:17.85,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The teacher praised her, so\N it must be above ninety percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.16,0:11:21.32,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Then, is it around ninety-two percent?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:24.49,0:11:25.70,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}What was that reaction?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:26.81,0:11:28.79,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Is it above ninety-five?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.31,0:11:31.51,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Ninety?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.97,0:11:35.11,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Ninety-two?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:40.19,0:11:42.92,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's faking it! I'm not gonna fall for it!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.92,0:11:45.68,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Такаги-сан would never make \Nher reaction so obvious!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.02,0:11:48.29,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Damn, she's mocking me.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:48.29,0:11:50.35,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm gonna do everything\N within my power to win this!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.13,0:11:53.85,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Focus more on her expression.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:56.12,0:11:57.65,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.15,0:12:03.20,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, it's nothing. It's just that
Dialogue: 0,0:12:03.69,0:12:06.41,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,we've been staring at each\N other for a while now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.00,0:12:12.51,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you turning away?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.51,0:12:17.12,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That's a cheap shot, Такаги-сан!\N I can't look at you after you said that!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.12,0:12:20.71,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Think... Just think... A hint of some sort...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.37,0:12:24.23,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}To make such a fake reaction,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.23,0:12:27.80,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it must mean Такаги-сан wants me\N to think she got ninety-two percent!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.19,0:12:31.32,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}That also means it won't be\N between ninety and ninety-four,
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.32,0:12:33.66,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}since they're within a two-percent difference!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:33.66,0:12:36.97,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Furthermore, the teacher praised\N her, so it's above ninety percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.97,0:12:39.78,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}And it's not a hundred percent, so...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.90,0:12:43.94,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it's between ninety-five and ninety-nine!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:44.34,0:12:47.49,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's flawless! Perfect victory!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:47.98,0:12:51.58,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Такаги-сан, you scored...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.99,0:12:53.79,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,ninety-seven percent!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:56.46,0:12:59.21,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Wrong. I got ninety-two percent.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.21,0:13:01.09,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Wh-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.18,0:13:04.01,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You don't trust me enough.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:04.01,0:13:07.30,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I gave you a three-point handicap\N on purpose for nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:18.94,0:13:22.94,Bookstore,Title 3,0000,0000,0000,,Bookstore
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.70,0:13:21.50,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,"Bookstore."
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:27.41,Unrequited,Manga(L),0000,0000,0000,,100% Unrequited Love
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:27.41,Fierce!!,Manga(L),0000,0000,0000,,Fierce!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:22.94,0:13:27.41,Ultimate Soccer!!,Manga(L),0000,0000,0000,,Ultimate Soccer!!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.91,0:13:32.29,Books,Sign,0000,0000,0000,,Books
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.58,0:13:32.29,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No one's coming. No one's coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:35.25,0:13:36.47,Main,Cashier,0000,0000,0000,,Welcome.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:39.15,0:13:40.92,Main,Cashier,0000,0000,0000,,It'll be 420 yen, ple—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:42.71,0:13:44.21,Main,Cashier,0000,0000,0000,,Exactly 420 yen.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.21,0:13:45.64,Main,Cashier,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like a cover—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.84,0:13:45.64,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.07,0:13:47.15,Main,Cashier,0000,0000,0000,,Would you like a bag—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:47.15,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.74,0:13:48.86,Main,Cashier,0000,0000,0000,,A rece—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.05,0:13:48.86,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,No, thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.17,0:13:51.66,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I got it!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.66,0:13:54.27,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Now, all I have to do is take\N this home and read it—
Dialogue: 0,0:13:54.52,0:13:56.46,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Morning, Нисиката.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:59.32,0:14:01.88,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}T-Такаги-сан? Why is she here?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.88,0:14:02.97,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I'm taking a walk.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:02.97,0:14:04.32,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Did she just read my mind?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.32,0:14:06.01,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,What are you doing, Нисиката?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.52,0:14:08.95,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Crap... If she sees this...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.60,0:14:12.01,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I have to play dumb no matter what.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.01,0:14:15.89,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Well, uh... I wanted to buy a book,\N but they were all out—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.50,0:14:19.42,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Wait, wait! Maybe she saw me at the register!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:23.88,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,I-I bought volume eleven of\N {\i1}Fierce!! Ultimate Soccer!!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.10,0:14:24.99,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}How's that?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:24.99,0:14:28.41,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's popular among boys, but girls\N aren't interested in that series at all.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:28.87,0:14:30.71,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It's a perfect answer!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.71,0:14:32.36,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I'm on a roll today—
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.36,0:14:34.22,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Fierce-Soccer{\i0}? Let me see. Let me see!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.22,0:14:35.18,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.43,0:14:38.75,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, but... I haven't read it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:38.75,0:14:40.40,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Can I at least see the cover?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.73,0:14:42.23,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,No, no! Definitely no!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.23,0:14:44.47,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,I haven't had the chance to look at it, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.47,0:14:45.78,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Then, let's look at it together.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:45.78,0:14:47.86,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,I like to look at it alone!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.16,0:14:49.07,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Aww...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.67,0:14:53.10,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I had no idea she'd be this interested.\N Such a dangerous person...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.10,0:14:55.29,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I better get away from her quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.90,0:14:57.50,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,See you later, Такаги-сан.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.16,0:15:05.09,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:05.69,0:15:08.72,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,We coincidentally ran into each other.\N Why don't we walk together for a bit?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:09.08,0:15:10.61,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,"Coincidentally"?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.51,0:15:13.54,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You don't always run into\N someone at a bookstore
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.54,0:15:16.09,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,this far from home so\N early in the morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:18.68,0:15:23.33,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}But to think there's something in\N this backpack I can't let her see,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:23.33,0:15:25.16,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}it's as though my heart's in my mouth.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.16,0:15:26.94,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I wish I were home already.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:29.34,0:15:30.86,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Нисиката.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.58,0:15:33.19,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Are you lying to me?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:37.49,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Are you lying?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.79,0:15:39.81,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, um...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.89,0:15:42.70,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You didn't buy {\i1}Fierce-Soccer{\i0}, did you?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.38,0:15:46.89,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You bought something so\N embarrassing you had to lie about it?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:46.89,0:15:48.85,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,No... Uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.45,0:15:51.30,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,It's just a girl's manga, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.69,0:15:53.76,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}100% Unrequited Love{\i0}?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.76,0:15:56.97,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,No, I mean, that {\i1}is {\i0}what I got...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.97,0:15:59.43,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,But how did you know?!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:59.87,0:16:02.25,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Well, I just happened to be passing by
Dialogue: 0,0:16:02.25,0:16:05.40,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,when I saw you at the register,\N and I saw the title as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.93,0:16:08.29,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She knew it all along and was playing with me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.29,0:16:10.16,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Is it because you like the anime?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.16,0:16:11.90,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I didn't know you read that kind of stuff.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.90,0:16:13.36,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Такаги-сан!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.16,0:16:17.04,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Please don't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:17.04,0:16:20.08,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Watching it on TV is one thing,\N but if people found out I'm actually
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.08,0:16:22.59,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,buying and reading the manga,\N I'll be a laughingstock.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:22.59,0:16:26.54,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, should I? I mean, you did lie to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.29,0:16:30.71,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I've never lied to you, you know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:32.09,0:16:34.01,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,All right, I won't tell.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.01,0:16:34.83,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.81,0:16:37.40,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,That easily?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.40,0:16:38.10,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,What?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.10,0:16:40.31,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,I'm serious. Seriously, don't tell anyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.65,0:16:42.47,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.47,0:16:45.53,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Seriously?! That was too easy, Такаги-сан!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.53,0:16:47.11,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You're so persistent...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.76,0:16:51.06,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, then how about this?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.93,0:16:55.01,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I'll tell you my secret.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.59,0:16:59.25,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You'll be somewhat at ease\N knowing my secret, too, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.79,0:17:02.16,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Uh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.83,0:17:04.88,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Then, lean closer.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.88,0:17:06.02,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.41,0:17:11.13,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I like you, Нисиката.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:16.38,0:17:17.18,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.69,0:17:19.89,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Huh?! Такаги-сан? Huh?!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:22.62,0:17:24.05,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You're bright red!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.05,0:17:26.81,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You blush so quickly, Нисиката.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.47,0:17:31.93,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Since you lied to me,\NI lied to you as payback.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:33.80,0:17:36.83,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, a lie... You startled me.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:36.83,0:17:38.36,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Yep, a lie.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:39.02,0:17:40.57,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Of course I'm lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.73,0:17:44.14,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I'm going this way, so see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.62,0:17:47.30,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Right. Bye-bye, see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:49.37,0:17:51.01,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}A lie, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:51.82,0:17:53.51,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, Нисиката.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.96,0:17:58.65,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I want to read {\i1}100% Unrequited Love{\i0}\N too, so can I borrow it next time?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.32,0:18:04.34,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Don't say it out loud, Такаги-сан!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:04.97,0:18:08.98,shelter,Title 4,0000,0000,0000,,Shelter from the Rain
Dialogue: 0,0:18:06.59,0:18:07.65,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,"Shelter from the Rain."
Dialogue: 0,0:18:10.75,0:18:13.06,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,It started raining so suddenly.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:13.72,0:18:15.32,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I wonder if it's going to stop soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:15.64,0:18:17.99,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Hmm, I don't know...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:19.58,0:18:22.24,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Aww, even my socks got wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.63,0:18:25.38,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,How about you, Нисиката?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:25.38,0:18:28.37,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I-I can kinda see through, Такаги-сан!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:29.28,0:18:30.08,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Are you listening?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:30.08,0:18:32.22,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, yeah, right...
Dialogue: 0,0:18:32.22,0:18:33.79,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Keep calm! Keep calm!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:33.79,0:18:37.20,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If she realizes I'm panicking,\N I'll be branded as a pervert!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.20,0:18:39.55,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah, I hope it'll stop soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:39.76,0:18:42.98,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,I wanna go home soon because there's\N an anime I wanna watch past five.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:42.98,0:18:45.51,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,It's {\i1}Fierce-Soccer{\i0}, by the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.68,0:18:48.90,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,The one you bought at the bookstore?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.90,0:18:52.02,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, wait. That was {\i1}100% Unrequited Love{\i0}.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:52.02,0:18:54.91,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Y-You promised you wouldn't say anything!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:54.91,0:18:57.81,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,But I can talk to you about it, right?\N You're the person in question, after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:59.86,0:19:01.41,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I hope it stops soon.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.63,0:19:05.28,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Uhh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.79,0:19:11.71,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Aww, it's a little wet.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:11.99,0:19:14.34,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Нисиката. Do you have your P.E. shirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.34,0:19:16.32,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Huh? Uh, yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.32,0:19:19.03,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Can I borrow it? I'll wash\N it and return it to you.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:19.03,0:19:20.40,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I want to change out of this.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.88,0:19:24.55,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Change out of it? To my P.E. shirt? Here?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:24.86,0:19:27.27,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah. My shirt's wet. I feel gross.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.89,0:19:28.84,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,But...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.84,0:19:32.04,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Besides, it seems like you're having\N trouble deciding where to look.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.04,0:19:33.27,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She noticed.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:34.33,0:19:35.61,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Can you turn the other way?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.61,0:19:36.97,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.22,0:19:41.07,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You managed to stay pretty dry, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.07,0:19:41.87,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.38,0:19:43.03,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,How?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:43.77,0:19:45.62,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, you used your bag as an umbrella?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:46.06,0:19:47.37,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Y-Yeah...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.55,0:19:51.70,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I see. I had to hold my bike.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.23,0:19:53.21,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Right...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.74,0:19:57.42,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You can look if you want.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.73,0:20:01.17,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Uh, Такаги-сан? What are you say—
Dialogue: 0,0:20:01.46,0:20:03.01,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I'm done changing.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.34,0:20:06.67,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Why are you flustered?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:07.42,0:20:09.10,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}She's toying with me!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:09.55,0:20:11.75,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, you want to make a bet
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.93,0:20:17.03,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,on whether or not the rain will stop\N by the time the town clock strikes five?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.45,0:20:19.61,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,The loser has to do\N anything the winner wants.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.89,0:20:20.72,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.72,0:20:21.99,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,What's your bet?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.42,0:20:23.76,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,The rain won't stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.18,0:20:25.89,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Then, I'll bet the rain will stop.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:27.98,0:20:30.41,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If the rain stops, I can go home\N and watch {\i0}Fierce-Soccer{\i1}.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:30.41,0:20:33.08,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}If the rain doesn't stop,\N I get to order Такаги-сан around.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:33.08,0:20:34.79,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I win either way!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.04,0:20:39.33,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I feel better now that I've changed my shirt.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:39.33,0:20:40.76,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Thanks, Нисиката.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:40.76,0:20:42.30,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Don't mention it.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.96,0:20:44.68,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,It smells kinda sweaty, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:44.68,0:20:47.21,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,It's summer. Of course it does!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.87,0:20:53.70,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The fabric that was on my body\N is touching Такаги-сан's.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.70,0:20:56.02,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}No! What am I thinking?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:56.94,0:20:57.84,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,A cat...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:57.84,0:20:58.65,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, hey.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:59.45,0:21:01.11,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Are you here to take shelter?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:01.38,0:21:02.37,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Come here.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:02.82,0:21:04.32,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,He's cute, but be careful.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:04.64,0:21:05.78,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,He scratches.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.18,0:21:11.06,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You want your shirt back?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:11.06,0:21:12.43,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,No, I'm fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.86,0:21:16.71,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Why don't you wear my P.E. shirt?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.01,0:21:17.61,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.61,0:21:20.47,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,It's a little wet, but it's better\N than what you're wearing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.98,0:21:26.76,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}The fabric that was touching\N Такаги-сан's body will be...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:27.34,0:21:28.45,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You done changing?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.64,0:21:31.97,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Don't look! Jeez!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:32.85,0:21:36.31,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}I feel as if I'm doing something naughty.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:38.01,0:21:39.27,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}It smells good.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:52.47,0:21:54.02,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,I guess I win.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:54.38,0:21:55.89,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,What should I make you do?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:57.25,0:22:00.67,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Oh, well. {\i1}Fierce-Soccer{\i0} will be\N waiting for me when I get home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.10,0:22:03.15,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,{\i1}Let's just get this over with\Nand run home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:03.69,0:22:04.81,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,Hey, Нисиката.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:06.67,0:22:09.59,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,It stopped raining, so let's go\N somewhere before we go home.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:09.83,0:22:11.49,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,But Такаги-сан, I...
Dialogue: 0,0:22:11.49,0:22:14.64,Main-Takagi,Такаги,0000,0000,0000,,You promised the loser\N would obey, right? Let's go!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.64,0:22:16.37,Main-Nishikata,Нисиката,0000,0000,0000,,Aww...
